metadata.name: village looked at Wang
metadata.description:
was a kind of hatred in his tone.



At the beginning, Wang Xian was admitted to the university, or a key university, and was rewarded by the town, so that he could grow up in eight villages. However, this boy quit his job in the big city and went to the village to start a breeding farm.



It's OK to have a farm, and the strange things you raise are acceptable, except that this guy ended up raising rats.
